About this item

  • Adhesive Metal Plate Repacement: Replace magnet plate perfectly and work well with magnetic cell phone holder and magnet car mount. NOTE: UGREEN sticky metal plates for phone magnet are not magnets, just the metal discs for magnet to adhere to.
  • Strong Sticky Adhesive: Applied with super strong adhesive sticker, UGREEN car phone mount plate sticks on the smartphone back securely. No worry of falling off. Please wait for 24 hours before using to make sure it sticks firmly.
  • Rectangle and Round Magnet Plates: Provide you more options to apply on multiple mobile phones and even mini tablets with 2 rectangle and 2 circular plates. Dimension of rectangle one is 1.8" x 2.6", round one 's diameter is 1.7 inch.
  • Easy to Attach: Simply stick this metal disc onto the back of your phone or put it between cellphone and its phone case. NOTE: For phone case thicker than 1mm, please stick it on the outside of the case to avoid interference with magnetism.
  • Ultra Thin and Slim: With 0.5 mm thickness, UGREEN slim metal plates for magnetic phone mount can be easily attached to your iphone. Its smooth surface with no sharp edges would not damage your fingers or smart phone.

Product Description

Why those magnetic car mounts only came with one single metal plate? Do I need to buy another new car mount?

No, just get extra spare metal plates.

UGREEN metal plates designed for magnetic car mounts solve your problem with no hassle.

With 2 pack rectangular and 2 pack round metal plates, it works perfectly as a spare especially when you have more than one mobile phone.

Make it possible to share one magnetic car mount holder or magnet phone stand with your family and friends.

Perfect Choice for High Quality

Strong Adhesive: Enable you to stick it securely onto the back of your phone.

Round Corners with No Sharps: Protect your devices and hands from scratches.

Slim and Portable: Rectangle plate dimension is 2.6" x 1.8" and round one's diameter is 1.7".

Easy to Use: Stick to the back of your phone or put it between your phone and the thin case.

Widely Compatibility: Fit for various magnetic car mount holders and smartphones even small tablets.

Read more

Installation Steps

Firstly clean the dust on the back of your phone. Make sure the surface of your phone back is dry and smooth.

Secondly uncover the sticker and stick the metal plate onto the surface. Adhere with finger or hand pressure on it for consistent 20 seconds.

Thirdly I suggest you wait for 24 hours before using to make sure the metal plate sticks firmly on your phone back.

If you want to remove it, please remember to use hair dryer blowing hot wind on it to melt the adhesive first.

Important Note

  • This product cannot apply to silicone or rubber phone case.
  • For phone case thicker than 1mm, we do suggest you stick it on the outside of the case to avoid interference with magnetism.
  • For wireless charging, please place metal plate away from wireless charging sensor on your phone back or place metal plate on phone case and remove case for wireless charging.
